===========================================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



02. GET /v2/entities/E1 to see E1/T1/A1=1
=========================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 70
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "A1": {
        "metadata": {},
        "type": "Number",
        "value": 1
    },
    "id": "E1",
    "type": "T1"
}


