}


09. Add an attribute A2=9 using POST /v2/op/update with APPEND_STRICT
=====================================================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



10. GET /v2/entities/E1 to see E1/T1/A1=7,A2=9
==============================================
